p.k: Take Your Seth to Work Day Seth's desire to help Nancy with her job at the hospital results in chaos when he without Nancy's knowledge plays doctor on sick Fancies. Seth has to admit his wrongdoing and listen to his mom in order to set things right.
p.d: This prehistoric comedy from Stephen Neary explores Fungietown through the whimsical quests of Seth, a young student at Fungietown Elementary.
